Top Dog is a game entry for the 2012 7-Day RogueLike comp. The game is written in Python 2.6 and the Doryen library.

The Story:

The Puppy has been kidnapped by the Fat Cat Mafioso. You travel from yard to yard, searching for the crafty Cats holding her hostage, meeting other animals along the way.

Keys:

The number keypad moves you up, down, sideways and diagonally.
VI-like movement is also supported.

7   8   9       y   k   u
4       6       h       l
1   2   3       b   j   n
    
press ? any time to see in-game help.

This game lives at:

    7drl.darknet.co.za

Woof! ^.^
